description: The US Supreme Court ruled in favor of the Republican National Committee and Wisconsin Republicans Monday, blocking a lower court ruling that gave voters an extra six days to submit their ballots from Election Day to April 13.
title: READ: Supreme Court decision on Wisconsin primary election
title_page: READ: Supreme Court decision on Wisconsin primary election - CNNPolitics
maintext: (CNN) The US Supreme Court ruled in favor of the Republican National Committee and Wisconsin Republicans Monday, blocking a lower court ruling that gave voters an extra six days to submit their ballots from Election Day to April 13.
